1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:01,640
Plaza del Colegio
del Patriarca.

2
00:00:01,640 --> 00:00:03,680
Pleno centro
de Valencia.

3
00:00:03,680 --> 00:00:05,560
Y ahi,
en una esquina...

4
00:00:05,560 --> 00:00:06,960
esto no me
lo esperaba.

5
00:00:06,960 --> 00:00:07,800
No os vayais.

6
00:00:07,800 --> 00:00:08,560
Hay mas.

7
00:00:08,560 --> 00:00:09,400
Es que...

8
00:00:09,400 --> 00:00:09,960
alguien por aqui

9
00:00:09,960 --> 00:00:11,760
necesita justo
lo que acabo de ver.

10
00:00:11,760 --> 00:00:12,280
Seguro.

11
00:00:12,280 --> 00:00:13,360
Pasa por esta plaza

12
00:00:13,360 --> 00:00:14,680
cada manana
camino al trabajo.

13
00:00:14,680 --> 00:00:16,480
Y no se va
a enterar nunca.

14
00:00:16,480 --> 00:00:18,240
Porque no hay
manera de saberlo.

15
00:00:18,240 --> 00:00:19,920
Dos personas
que se necesitan

16
00:00:19,920 --> 00:00:21,200
y que no se van
a cruzar.

17
00:00:21,200 --> 00:00:22,840
O no se iban
a cruzar.

18
00:00:22,840 --> 00:00:23,880
Saco el movil.

19
00:00:23,880 --> 00:00:24,560
Givore.

20
00:00:24,560 --> 00:00:26,360
Foto,
dos palabras,
publico.

21
00:00:26,360 --> 00:00:27,400
Medio minuto.

22
00:00:27,400 --> 00:00:28,480
Y ahora mirad
lo que habia.

23
00:00:28,480 --> 00:00:29,360
Una silla de oficina

24
00:00:29,360 --> 00:00:29,840
en buen estado.

25
00:00:29,840 --> 00:00:32,400
Con ruedas,
regulable,

26
00:00:32,400 --> 00:00:33,560
de esas que
en tienda

27
00:00:33,560 --> 00:00:34,560
cuestan lo suyo.

28
00:00:34,560 --> 00:00:35,600
Y al lado...

29
00:00:35,600 --> 00:00:36,600
un carrito de compras

30
00:00:36,600 --> 00:00:37,640
que va perfecto.

31
00:00:37,640 --> 00:00:39,040
Los dos, ahi,
junto a la plaza.

32
00:00:39,040 --> 00:00:41,360
Todo el centro
los puede ver ahora.

33
00:00:41,360 --> 00:00:42,560
Alguien va a abrir
la app

34
00:00:42,560 --> 00:00:43,600
y va a pensar...

35
00:00:43,600 --> 00:00:45,160
justo lo que
necesitaba.

36
00:00:45,160 --> 00:00:46,600
El sol cae
sobre la plaza.

37
00:00:46,600 --> 00:00:48,520
Otro paseo,
otro hallazgo.

38
00:00:48,520 --> 00:00:49,080
Si quereis ver

39
00:00:49,080 --> 00:00:50,640
que sale la
proxima semana...

40
00:00:50,640 --> 00:00:51,400
seguidme.

41
00:00:51,400 --> 00:00:52,160
Nos vemos.

